data.description: 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath townhome conveniently located in heart of West Linn, close to Tanner Creek Park, Safeway grocery store, shops and restaurants. Great room floor plan on main floor with newer Pergo floors. Updated kitchen has island, newer shaker cabinets, newer quartz counters and stainless-steel appliances. Slider off kitchen/dining area opens to deck and fenced back yard perfect for entertaining. Bedroom/office on the main with half bath. Primary bedroom upstairs with ensuite bathroom with newer double vanity and vinyl tile flooring. Built-in desk upstairs hallway perfect for remote work. Two bedrooms with vaulted ceilings and full bath upstairs. Laundry upstairs. Finished and newly carpeted lower level with tall ceilings. Double pained, vinyl windows and freshly painted throughout. New roof, skylight, gutters, porch staining and exterior paint were all completed in 2022. No rental cap!
